  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Bel Lenora is a world where people are born with magic at their command. Years ago, a single man walked the land with no magic in his veins. He brought death and tragedy in his wake and was banished by a brave General at a great cost. It has been fifteen years since his banishment and once again, a young man with no magic walks the land of Bel Lenora.\n\nJoin Kairu, a young knight, born with a cursed spirit...",
